1503
01:31:29,060 --> 01:31:31,320
So I was inspired to create something similar.

1504
01:31:35,930 --> 01:31:39,030
Contender Lee Hye Sung is a real foodie.

1505
01:31:39,100 --> 01:31:41,269
She really knows how to target the public,

1506
01:31:41,270 --> 01:31:43,569
