1518
01:32:28,650 --> 01:32:30,180
Why is the temperature so high?

1519
01:32:36,490 --> 01:32:38,490
Why did it go up so high?

1520
01:32:38,960 --> 01:32:41,630
It's 150, 140...

1521
01:32:45,400 --> 01:32:46,670
