1522
01:32:48,570 --> 01:32:49,570
- Gosh. - Oh, no.

1523
01:32:49,571 --> 01:32:51,799
- What's wrong? - Contender Lee Hye Sung...

1524
01:32:51,800 --> 01:32:53,339
