1562
01:34:52,060 --> 01:34:54,130
Okay, let's just use three.

1563
01:34:56,130 --> 01:34:57,930
It's fine. You can still do it.

1564
01:34:59,170 --> 01:35:01,429
Baking is all about the right temperature...

1565
01:35:01,430 --> 01:35:03,700
